xxl.core.math.statistics.parametric.aggregates

Class ReservoirSample.AbstractStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.math.statistics.parametric.aggregates.ReservoirSample.AbstractStrategy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReservoirSample.ReservoirSamplingStrategy
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReservoirSample.RType, ReservoirSample.XType, ReservoirSample.ZType
    Enclosing class:
    ReservoirSample

    public abstract static class ReservoirSample.AbstractStrategy
extends Object
implements ReservoirSample.ReservoirSamplingStrategy
    This class provides a preimplementation of the ReservoirSamplingStrategy interface to minimize the effort required to implement this interface. For further informations see ReservoirSampler.

    • Method Detail

      • invoke

        public int invoke()
        Preimplementation of the invoke-method to compute the skip value for the sampling strategy. One only needs to implement computeSkip and computePos to fulfill the requirements of reservoir sampling.
        Specified by:
        invoke in interface ReservoirSample.ReservoirSamplingStrategy
        Returns:
        computed position where to store the currently treated object in the used reservoir. If the given position exceeds the bounds of the reservoir the element has to be skipped.
